- He didn't mean to die.
- Fair.

508
00:25:02.542 --> 00:25:05.045
But you don't know
how your story was gonna end.

509
00:25:05.670 --> 00:25:08.298
and someone just ripped
those pages out of your book.

510
00:25:10.008 --> 00:25:10.842
Right.

511
00:25:11.384 --> 00:25:14.846
Maybe he was gonna tell you or apologize.

512
00:25:15.597 --> 00:25:16.556
Or leave me.

513
00:25:18.016 --> 00:25:19.142
He did leave you.

514
00:25:22.062 --> 00:25:23.647
Yeah.

515
00:25:24.523 --> 00:25:27.108
Believe it or not. what I'm hearing...

516
00:25:28.485 --> 00:25:30.612
is that you really loved him.

517
00:25:37.452 --> 00:25:38.328
Yeah.

518
00:25:40.914 --> 00:25:42.415
Yeah.

519
00:25:47.462 --> 00:25:48.713
Do you have any cigarettes?

520
00:25:50.006 --> 00:25:50.840
No.

521
00:26:06.439 --> 00:26:07.482
Oh. shoot.

522
00:26:07.816 --> 00:26:09.276
Oh!

523
00:26:18.868 --> 00:26:19.953
Oh. my God...

524
00:26:51.151 --> 00:26:52.110
Hi.

525
00:26:53.403 --> 00:26:54.446
Hi.

526
00:26:56.781 --> 00:26:57.616
Are you okay?

527
00:26:59.367 --> 00:27:00.493
No.

528
00:27:03.997 --> 00:27:05.081
How was your night?

529
00:27:05.457 --> 00:27:09.252
Um. it was... maybe better than yours?

530
00:27:12.380 --> 00:27:14.549
I need to get my shit together. Judy.

531
00:27:15.634 --> 00:27:17.594
- Okay.
- For my boys.

532
00:27:19.179 --> 00:27:20.138
Okay.

533
00:27:21.473 --> 00:27:23.683
But there's no escaping it. It's just...

534
00:27:25.560 --> 00:27:28.813
It's. like. wherever you go.
there you are. You know?

535
00:27:31.024 --> 00:27:31.900
Yeah.

536
00:27:33.360 --> 00:27:36.529
Which just... sucks.

537
00:27:40.533 --> 00:27:42.285
I wish you didn't feel like that.

538
00:27:43.745 --> 00:27:44.704
Well. I do.

539
00:27:46.748 --> 00:27:49.501
Because someone ripped my life apart.

540
00:27:54.047 --> 00:27:55.215
I hate that person.

541
00:28:06.351 --> 00:28:07.185
Hi.

542
00:28:08.144 --> 00:28:09.062
Hey.

543
00:28:10.063 --> 00:28:11.064
This is my friend. Jen.

544
00:28:14.192 --> 00:28:16.653
I usually look a little better than this.

545
00:28:18.113 --> 00:28:19.030
Hello. friend.

546
00:28:19.239 --> 00:28:20.573
This is Nick.

547
00:28:21.741 --> 00:28:22.742
Hi. Nick.

548
00:28:29.833 --> 00:28:30.709
He's a cop.

549
00:28:33.753 --> 00:28:35.797
A detective. actually.

550
00:28:42.762 --> 00:28:44.222
You ever solve a hit-and-run?

551
00:28:48.226 --> 00:28:49.102
Yes.
